1945175928.text: "Confirming drug potency, we observe that upon MEK specific inhibitors U0126 and AZD6244 phosphorylation of ERK1/2 -the target of MEK1- is blocked, while upon multi specific kinase inhibitor Sorafenib MEK1 phosphorylation decreases."
